headline: Textron Secures a $276.8M Contract to Supply T-54A Training Aircraft
summary: TXT secures a $276.8 million contract for the production and delivery of 26 T-54A trainer aircraft and other support equipment.

headline: Peruvian Air Force Receives Its First Aeromedical Evacuation-Equipped Beechcraft King Air 360CHW
summary: WICHITA, Kan., November 19, 2024--Textron Aviation today announced it delivered the first of two multi-mission Beechcraft King Air 360CHW aircraft to the Peruvian Air Force. The King Air 360CHW is cargo door equipped and fitted for heavy weight operation.
